39:45.350 --> 39:47.452 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But she wants to remain in her
home as long
as possible.

39:47.485 --> 39:50.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARVIE JEAN DARDEN, Oneva
Client: After I
had the stroke, I couldn't do
what I had done

39:50.788 --> 39:52.690 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
before.

39:52.724 --> 39:59.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I also worried about different
people that
we didn't know coming in to the
home and everything.

39:59.631 --> 40:05.937 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
APRIL BROWN: But since Oneva
introduced Mrs.
Darden to Seadawn Thomas (ph)
those problems

40:05.970 --> 40:07.205 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
have been solved.

40:07.238 --> 40:10.375 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARVIE JEAN DARDEN: She's more
than a caregiver.

40:10.408 --> 40:14.245 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You know, I feel like she's a
friend.

40:14.279 --> 40:18.583 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
APRIL BROWN: Several of Mrs.
Darden's adult
children live nearby, but have
busy lives

40:18.616 --> 40:21.819 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and children of their own.

40:21.853 --> 40:26.391 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Anita Darden Gardyne is one of
them, and part
of the so-called sandwich
generation, with

40:26.424 --> 40:28.793 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
elder and child care needs.

40:28.826 --> 40:33.598 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She has an 11-year old daughter,
and Marvie
Jean is her mother.

40:33.631 --> 40:37.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Gardyne realized many others had
the same
issues, so, in 2014, she came up
with the

40:38.002 --> 40:44.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
idea for Oneva, a service
providing FBI-background-checked
care providers that customers
can learn more

40:44.509 --> 40:46.644 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
about before they ever enter the
home.

40:46.678 --> 40:47.812 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ZOLA BOWIE: Well, I'm Zola.

40:47.845 --> 40:49.614 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I'm an Oneva caregiver.

40:49.647 --> 40:53.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
APRIL BROWN: Gardyne's business
currently
provides helpers for her
parents, the Santoses

40:53.918 --> 40:55.520 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and 60 other clients.

40:55.553 --> 40:59.557 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But being an African-American
woman entrepreneur
