lick envelopes

50:10.975 --> 50:11.942 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for Hillary.

50:11.976 --> 50:13.010 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Do they lick envelopes anymore?

50:13.043 --> 50:14.378 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: I don't think so.

50:14.411 --> 50:17.014 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAUREEN DOWD: Send e-mails for
Hillary, because
they're so nasty.

50:17.047 --> 50:19.483 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, a lot of that has been
stirred up.

50:19.516 --> 50:25.856 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, on the other hand, I think
she would
be better off not calling sexism
and modeling

50:25.890 --> 50:28.626 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
herself on the way Obama didn't
call racism.

50:28.659 --> 50:32.796 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Who would you say
you have admired
over the years in politics?

50:32.830 --> 50:35.065 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You speak kindly of George H.W.
Bush.

50:35.099 --> 50:37.034 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You speak kindly of Joe Biden.

50:37.067 --> 50:38.836 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAUREEN DOWD: Yes.

50:38.869 --> 50:44.608 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's hard, because I think I
don't really
want to be the kind of
economist, like Stewart

50:44.642 --> 50:49.580 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Alsop in the old days, or Scotty
Reston, who
really wanted to be friends with
politicians

50:49.613 --> 50:51.348 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and go to dinner parties with
them.

50:51.382 --> 50:57.254 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I mean, I think of myself as the
watchdog,
which creates problems sometimes
with "Times"

50:57.288 --> 51:00.291 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
readers, because I'm not coming
from the left
or the right.

51:00.324 --> 51:02.626 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I'm treating it more like a
political reporter.

51:02.660 --> 51:06.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: You are a Washington
native, something
a lot of people don't know about
you.

51:06.430 --> 51:11.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So you have watched the city not
only as a
collection of marble buildings,
but also as

51:11.535 --> 51:13.404 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
a community.

51:13.437 --> 51:18.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How has politics changed, how
has Washington
changed in your years as an
armchair observer,

51:18.909 --> 51:19.877 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
as it were?

51:19.910 --> 51:21.645 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAUREEN DOWD: Oh.

51:21.679 --> 51:28.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Well, you know, when I went to
see George
H.W. Bush for lunch a few years
ago, I think

51:28.886 --> 51:36.460 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he was just appalled at what had
happened,
because he was a bipartisan, and
he believed

51:36.493 --> 51:39.196 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in everyone working together and
civility.

51:39.229 --> 51:44.335 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so I think it was very hard
for him to
even fathom the kind of politics
that is being

51:44.368 --> 51:46.036 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
played nowadays.

51:46.070 --> 51:50.274 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I hope he doesn't tune in to
the debates
because he can't stand Donald
Trump.

51:50.307 --> 51:53.777 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He called him an epithet when I
was at lunch
with him.

51:53.811 --> 51:55.112 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Oh, my.

51:55.145 --> 51:59.049 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAUREEN DOWD: And that was
before Donald Trump
eviscerated Jeb.

51:59.083 --> 52:01.585 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So, it's much coarser.

52:01.618 --> 52:07.458 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I'm not sure if what that
leads to is
a lot of other celebrities
jumping in, because

52:07.491 --> 52:12.730 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
